title: WinX DVD Copy Pro v3.5.09 Final + Key - CORE
description:
WinX DVD Copy Pro is an advanced application designed to copy DVDs without any quality loss. WinX DVD Copy Pro is designed to bring you all-new DVD backup experience.
This up-to-date DVD copy software can help you decrypt & backup DVD to DVD disc, DVD to ISO, as well as copy DVD to single MPEG2 file with original video tracks and original surround AC3 audio.
Without the need of packing with any third party DVD decrypter, WinX DVD Copy Pro has unlimited access to all protected DVDs. It flawlessly removes DVD region code, CSS Encryption, UOPs, and even the most complicated Disney X-project DRM.

Processor: 1GHz Intel/AMD processor or above
RAM: 256MB RAM (512MB or above recommended)
Free Hard Disk: 100MB space for installation
Graphic Card: 256MB RAM (512MB or above recommended)
DVD-ROM drive
